  "remarks": "\nMania is an involved person within the meaning of the Bosnia and Herzegovina (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2020 in that, by promoting the celebration of Republika Srpska (RS) Day on 9 January 2024, it is or has been involved in undermining or threatening the constitutional order of Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH). \n",
